summary: A simple interior for those of us who need low lag areas to use showracemenu.
descriptionHtml:
[color=gray]This is a simple mod is for people who use console regularly. (showracemenu, coc [place here] commands) 

If anyone still hasn\'t, I highly suggest [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/33526/?]this mod[/url] to fix those nasty CTDs upon using the showracemenu command.
___________ _____ _____ ___ ___ __ _


[size=5]I find that Skyrim eats up my memory use, and makes it nearly impossible to use showracemenu in open areas, so I sat down for about 30 minutes and put together a quick esp I figured other people might want.[/size]

____________ ____ ____ ___ ____ __ _ 

The interior isn\'t closed, and the lighting isn\'t too bright or too dark for the best results. When you face the light, you can see some rolling clouds I added in the background as an afterthought. The music inside is the Sovngarde Chant.

Open the console and type \"coc meincell\" to be transported to the cell. \"Coc whiterun\" will get you out. (Main)  [/color]

There is now a map marker and trapdoor in Falkreath you can use to get there.
author: Wyn Xombii
